creator: Silver Dollar City Attractions
descriptionHtml:
Discover Silver Dollar City at your fingertips like never before!

An internationally awarded theme park in Branson, Missouri, Silver Dollar City offers an incredible experience for the entire family, including over 40 rides and attractions, 100 resident craftsmen, world-class seasonal festivals and award-winning shows and food — all sitting above one of Missouri's deepest caves!

The Silver Dollar City App ensures you maximize every moment with unique features such as:

Wayfinding Map:
Use our interactive Wayfinding map to navigate yourself throughout Silver Dollar City. Get Directions to Rides, Attractions, Theaters and Shops to experience Silver Dollar City to the fullest!

Show Schedules:
Never miss a show with our Show Schedule feature! The Show Schedule displays artists, acts and performance times at each theater and venue throughout Silver Dollar City.

Ride Wait Times:
Make the most of each moment with Ride Wait Times! Ride Wait Times allow you to plan your day by showing you the estimated wait time for each ride.

Exclusive Offers:
Reap the benefits of Exclusive Offers for Silver Dollar City app users — only available to you when you download.

Customize Your Experience:
Chart your day your way. Create customized lists of all the Rides, Attractions, Shows and Restaurants you wish to experience during your visit, and cross them off your list once you've seen them!

title: Silver Dollar City

creator: Herschend Family Entertainment
descriptionHtml:
Download, use and enjoy this app to experience your Ozark Mountain adventure like never before.

Silver Dollar City Attractions offers an incredible experience for the entire family including an award-winning theme park featuring record-breaking coasters and one-of-a-kind rides, world-class festivals spring through Christmas, demonstrations from master craftsmen, unique dining and more. For summer fun, explore a 13-acre water park filled with exhilarating slides & family attractions. And discover beautiful Table Rock Lake aboard an 1890s-style paddle wheeler complete with a delicious 3-course meal and exciting stage show.

The Silver Dollar City Attractions App ensures you maximize every moment with unique features such as:

Information For All Parks & Attractions - Explore our entire destination, including Silver Dollar City, White Water, the Showboat Branson Belle and other area experiences.

Up-To-Date Hours, Schedules & Ride Wait Times - Make the most of each moment with real-time updates to our hours of operation, show schedules and estimated ride wait times for our most popular attractions.

Maps & Wayfinding - Navigate with the interactive GPS-enabled map to find the best routes to rides, dining, shops, crafts, theaters and more. View accessibility information, restaurant menus, shop offerings, and more—across the destination or at a specific property.

My Silver Dollar City Account Integration - Link your day tickets, Season Passes, Bring-A-Friend tickets, add-ons and more for quick access. Utilize the app itself or add your tickets and passes to your phone’s digital wallet for easy entry and use at the parks.
descriptionShort: The Official Silver Dollar City App

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Silver Dollar City Attractions app has been expanded to include information on all properties within our Ozark Mountain destination, including the theme park, water park, dinner cruise and other area experiences.
1. Redesigned home screen featuring the information you want most
2. New curated adventure lists with activities perfect for every age and member of the family
3. Expanded wayfinding and directions across our entire destination
4. Enhanced schedules for each show and venue

title: Silver Dollar City Attractions

creator: Herschend Family Entertainment
descriptionHtml:
Download, use and enjoy this app to experience your Ozark Mountain adventure like never before.

Silver Dollar City Attractions offers an incredible experience for the entire family including an award-winning theme park featuring record-breaking coasters and one-of-a-kind rides, world-class festivals spring through Christmas, demonstrations from master craftsmen, unique dining and more. For summer fun, explore a 13-acre water park filled with exhilarating slides & family attractions. And discover beautiful Table Rock Lake aboard an 1890s-style paddle wheeler complete with a delicious 3-course meal and exciting stage show.

The Silver Dollar City Attractions App ensures you maximize every moment with unique features such as:

Information For All Parks & Attractions - Explore our entire destination, including Silver Dollar City, White Water, the Showboat Branson Belle and other area experiences.

Up-To-Date Hours, Schedules & Ride Wait Times - Make the most of each moment with real-time updates to our hours of operation, show schedules and estimated ride wait times for our most popular attractions.

Maps & Wayfinding - Navigate with the interactive GPS-enabled map to find the best routes to rides, dining, shops, crafts, theaters and more. View accessibility information, restaurant menus, shop offerings, and more—across the destination or at a specific property.

My Silver Dollar City Account Integration - Link your day tickets, Season Passes, Bring-A-Friend tickets, add-ons and more for quick access. Utilize the app itself or add your tickets and passes to your phone’s digital wallet for easy entry and use at the parks.
